Subject: [PATCH 07/16] media: cadence: csi2rx: Set the STOP bit when stopping a stream
Date:   Tue, 30 Mar 2021 23:03:39 +0530
Message-ID: <20210330173348.30135-8-p.yadav@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.0
